  "id": "RAW_eace4f",
  "title": "扣子开源，三天揽获 1.5W GitHub Star",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&mid=2247515738&idx=1&sn=908b3881f8b9144b1f7b4bb05da8a117",
  "date": "2025-07-31 10:05:00",
  "author": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "siteName": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <div style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><div style=\"line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100032087\" data-ratio=\"0.4255556\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b04a973e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOhvmseUxpEKRBMWTOZAZibxpTPFEnSweQZ2bqP07woVT1K8kGc7woE6CEibwTEfmcPN8Haib9mtVQDTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: unset;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年，AI Agent赛道进入爆发式增长的新阶段。在基础模型能力进步的推动下，AI Agent正在从「概念验证」走向「大规模部署」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了让更多开发者和组织受益于前沿技术，真正降低AI Agent应用开发的门槛，我们在 7 月 26 日将 Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop 正式开源至 GitHub。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">短短三天内</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">，Coze Studio 已获得 1.1W Star， Coze Loop 已获得 4K Star。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <div style=\"line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100032088\" data-ratio=\"0.4351852\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=af874afd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOhvmseUxpEKRBMWTOZAZibxpjG7Cda5rmw6xmCjia9AUy3eok5VCZRFolNlktCckqjl9mpgTeyGIxUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前， Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop 共揽获1.7W+ Star。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: unset;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Studio 源自服务了上万家企业、数百万开发者的「扣子开发平台」，我们将它的核心引擎完全开放。它是一个一站式的 AI Agent 可视化开发工具，让 AI Agent 的创建、调试和部署变得前所未有的简单。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 8px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;width: 100%;border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);text-align: justify;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Studio:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/coze-dev/coze-studio\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/coze-dev/coze-studio</a></span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: unset;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Loop 脱胎于企业级的 AI Agent 全生命周期调优平台「扣子罗盘」，聚焦 Agent 从开发到运维的全链路管理，旨在成为每一位开发者的 AI Agent 「智能运维官」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 8px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;width: 100%;border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);text-align: justify;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Loop:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/coze-dev/coze-loop\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/coze-dev/coze-loop</a></span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: unset;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个里程碑，属于每一位 Coze 关注者、反馈者和贡献者！</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子开源了哪些核心功能？</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子包含四款子产品：「扣子空间」、「扣子开发平台」、「扣子罗盘」 及 Eino。在本次开源中，我们选择了平台最核心的两个项目：Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Studio</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Studio 此次开源的核心功能包括：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">完整的工作流（Workflow）引擎：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">只需拖拽节点，就能轻松编排出复杂的业务逻辑。无论是简单的问答机器人，还是需要执行多步任务的 Agent，都能轻松实现。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">插件（Plugin）核心框架：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">我们开放了插件的定义、调用与管理机制。你可以便捷地将任何第三方 API 或私有能力封装成插件，无限扩展 Agent 的能力边界。我们还提供了官方开源插件作为参考，让你立刻上手。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">开箱即用的开发环境：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">你只需一键部署，即可获得一个功能完备的 Agent 开发平台，包括创建、调试、版本管理等全套界面，让你专注于创造本身。</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Loop</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Loop 此次开源的核心功能包括：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt 开发：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">提供从编写、调试、一键优化到版本管理的强大能力，让你的 Prompt 工程化、系统化。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">多维度评测：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">AI 的效果好坏不再凭感觉。Coze Loop 提供系统化的评测能力，能从准确性、简洁性、合规性等多个维度，自动化地评估 Prompt 和 Agent 的输出质量。支持Agent轨迹、Agent Tool选择质量等Agent细粒度的评测。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">全链路可观测性：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Agent 的每一次执行过程都尽在掌握。我们提供覆盖全过程的可视化观测能力，详细记录每个环节的处理细节与状态，让 Debug 不再是大海捞针。</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子为何选择Apache 2.0开源协议？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: unset;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源可以吸引全球更多开发者参与，构建丰富的插件和应用生态，是凝聚开发者智慧、加速生态繁荣的最佳路径。此次Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop采用 Apache 2.0 开源许可证，并且没有任何附加协议。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">商业友好：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">你可以自由地用于商业化产品，无任何附加条款。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">专利授权：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">我们提供明确的专利授权，为你扫清后顾之忧。</span></p></li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">社区共建：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">我们期待与全球开发者一起，共同定义和构建 AI Agent 的未来。</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Star us on GitHub, Build with Coze!</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: unset;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源，是扣子迈出的重要一步，但仅仅是一个开始。一个伟大的开源项目离不开社区的共创，AI Agent 的未来同样属于每一位开发者和创造者。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们诚挚地邀请每一位对 AI Agent 技术充满热情的开发者加入，无论是提交一个 PR、提出一个 Issue，还是在社群里分享一个灵感与想法，都将是最宝贵的支持。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin: 20px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 24px;background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);border-radius: 10px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 250) 1px 1px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">邮箱：</span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">opensource-studio@coze.cn</span></span></p></li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Discord Server：</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/sTVN9EVS4B\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/sTVN9EVS4B</a></span></span></p></li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">飞书群：</span></span></strong></span></p></li>\n     </ul>\n     <p></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100032085\" data-ratio=\"1.0842593\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=212e1f1a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOhvmseUxpEKRBMWTOZAZibxpYLUBPBN2x15uOOic37cAsLXcmzqqz4qRmsH33Q3E6FWbdEu0eI44weA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Studio</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin: 30px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 24px;background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);border-radius: 10px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 250) 1px 1px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">邮箱：</span></span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">opensource-loop@coze.cn</span></span></p></li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Discord Server：</span></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/sTVN9EVS4B\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/sTVN9EVS4B</a></span></p></li>\n      <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 116, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">飞书群：</span></span></strong></p></li>\n     </ul>\n     <p></p>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100032086\" data-ratio=\"1.0842593\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54b2b60a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5EcwYhllQOhvmseUxpEKRBMWTOZAZibxpVrRcfp2nMicbQQ1ZhHPLEnQBGgFicekYvb7NmBtUofmq18iazjG2EJOmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Coze Loop</span></p></div></div></div></div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "字节跳动将 AI Agent 开发平台扣子（Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop）开源，三天内获得 1.7W+ Star，旨在降低 AI Agent 应用开发门槛。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "字节跳动将 AI Agent 开发平台扣子（Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop）开源，三天内获得 1.7W+ Star，旨在降低 AI Agent 应用开发门槛。",
  "summary": "文章宣布字节跳动将其 AI Agent 开发平台“扣子”（Coze Studio 和 Coze Loop）正式开源，并在三天内迅速获得超过 1.7 万 GitHub Star。Coze Studio 是一个一站式 AI Agent 可视化开发工具，包含完整的工作流引擎、插件核心框架和开箱即用的开发环境，简化了 Agent 的创建与部署。Coze Loop 则聚焦 Agent 全生命周期调优，提供 Prompt 开发、多维度评测及全链路可观测性功能。文章强调开源旨在降低 AI Agent 应用开发门槛，吸引全球开发者共同构建生态，并采用了商业友好的 Apache 2.0 开源协议。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
